byline.contributor: James C. McKinley Jr. contributed reporting. Susan C. Beachy contributed research.

lead_paragraph: Zunilda Rosario was charged in the fatal 1990 shooting of Juan Deleon, with whom she had two children, after his roommate spoke to the police.

headline.main: Arrest in Manhattan Murder After Witness Talks to Police 26 Years Later
